dct_title_s: Asia Minor & Armenia [cartographic material] : to illustrate routes of Mr. Ainsworth, Mr. Brant, Mr. Suter, & Lord Pollington. (geotiff)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Mr. Ainsworth's, Mr. Brant's, Mr. Suter's, and Lord Pollington's routes are colored. "The eastern portion of the Map, from observations by Mr. A. G. Glascott, R.N." From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 10 (1840), pp. 275-454, 489-529; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.10 1840
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1840.
